title: [A Small Garden]
description: The short and stocky building housing the local smithy rises up from this verdant garden.  Lamp light shines from the windows of the building.  Slightly off the path resides a large wrought iron sign with ivy growing around its legs.  Small, spherical bushes line the cobbled walkway leading to the entrance of the building.

The short and stocky building housing the local smithy rises up from this verdant garden.  A red brick chimney puffs clouds of thick, black smoke.  Slightly off the path resides a large wrought iron sign with ivy growing around its legs.  Small, spherical bushes line the cobbled walkway leading to the entrance of the building.
